ad: It is a structure variable of type struct m, which has two members: n and o.
ae: It is an integer variable that is assigned the value of ad.o.
r: It is an integer variable that is assigned the result of the expression ad.o % (~s_sign / ae).
s_sign: It is a static integer variable with the value -5.
s_unsigned: It is an integer variable with the value 5.
